data.description: Welcome to 5088 Woodstock Dr, a charming ranch home nestled in the heart of the  Oakwood Village neighborhood in Swartz Creek/Gaines Township!   As you step inside, you'll immediately appreciate the warm ambiance created by the rich wood floors that flow seamlessly throughout the entire home. The well-designed floor plan includes three bedrooms, providing ample space for relaxation and privacy. With three full baths, morning routines and evening unwinding become a breeze for the whole family.  This home offers an on-demand water heater that ensures a continuous supply of hot water for your convenience. The kitchen, overlooks the spacious yard and stamped covered patio – an ideal spot for entertaining or simply enjoying a quiet evening outdoors.  One of the highlights of 5088 Woodstock Dr is the fenced-in yard, providing a private oasis for both children and pets to play freely. Picture perfect for summer barbecues, gardening, or just relaxing in your own piece of paradise. In ground sprinkler system!   For those seeking additional space, the finished basement provides endless possibilities – whether it's a home office, recreation room, or a cozy retreat for guests, this versatile area is yours to customize. The downstairs bathroom has a new Kohler walk in Jacuzzi tub. The electrical box is updated and there is a separate gas wall furnace.  Schedule your showing today and envision a future filled with cherished memories in this delightful residence.
